oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sam Masengill's shoe shop
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Sam Masengill's shoe shop. Shows Sam Massengill, who operated the shop for 47 years.
Sam S. Masengill (1882-1962) was married to Harriet Adeline "Hattie" Henson Masengill (1883-1985).
